1997;;Eight Days a Week;;American;;Michael Davis;;Keri Russell;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eight_Days_a_Week_(film);;Peter (Joshua Schaefer) is infatuated with his childhood friend and next-door neighbor Erica (Keri Russell). Based on advice from his grandfather, Peter decides to camp on Erica's lawn until she realizes that she loves him. During his summer-long wait, he frequently comments on their neighborhood.